'''哈里·莱斯利·皮克林'''（{{lang-en|Harry Leslie Pickering}}；{{bd|1998年|12月29日}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是左邊衛，現效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[布萊克本流浪者足球俱樂部|布力般流浪]]。

==足球生涯==
哈里·皮克林在克魯學習踢球，2016年3月與球會簽下職業合約<ref name="Sharpe-10Mar2016">{{cite news|last1=Sharpe|first1=Rich|title=Crewe Alexandra: Alex tie promising Academy pair to professional deals|url=http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/crewe-alexandra-alex-tie-promising-academy-pair/story-28899255-detail/story.html|accessdate=2017-04-22|work=Sentinel|date=2016-03-10}}</ref><ref name="CAnet-10Mar2016">{{cite web|title=Pickering & Dale Sign Professional Terms|url=http://www.crewealex.net/news/article/pickering-dale-sign-professional-terms-3000151.aspx|website=CreweAlex.net|accessdate=2017-04-22}}</ref>。2017年4月22日對[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|莱顿东方]]，他在63分鐘換入，首次在職業聯賽上場<ref name="BBC-22Apr2017">{{cite news|title=Crewe Alexandra 3-0 Leyton Orient|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39605702|accessdate=2017-04-23|work=BBC Sport|date=2017-04-22|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112040030/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39605702|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年2月24日作客[[v|林肯城]]，他主射自由球破網，助球隊追成平手，是他首顆職業生涯進球，使球隊最後以4-1反勝<ref name="BBC-24Feb2018">{{cite news |title=Lincoln City 1-4 Crewe Alexandra |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43093801 |access-date=2021-01-12 |work=BBC Sport |date=2018-02-24 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814192728/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43093801 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年4月，他與球隊簽下一份新的3年合約，並附有一年延長權<ref name="CAnet-12Apr2018">{{cite news|title=Contract: Pickering Puts Pen-To-Paper On Long-Term Deal|url=https://www.crewealex.net/news/2018/april/contract-pickering-puts-pen-to-paper-on-long-term-deal/|accessdate=2018-04-13|work=CreweAlex.net|date=2018-04-12|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813140248/https://www.crewealex.net/news/2018/april/contract-pickering-puts-pen-to-paper-on-long-term-deal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月21日對[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|科尔切斯特联]]的比賽期間受傷，使他需要缺席賽場，養傷一個月<ref name="Wilson-28Aug2018">{{cite news |last1=Wilson |first1=Rob |title=Pickering Also Ruled Out For Extended Period With Hamstring Tear |url=https://www.crewealex.net/news/2018/august/pickering-hamstring-tear/ |accessdate=2018-08-28 |work=CreweAlex.net |date=2018-08-28 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809170514/https://www.crewealex.net/news/2018/august/pickering-hamstring-tear/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年9月，他與球會再簽下一份新的3年合約<ref name="CAnet-4Sep2020">{{cite web |title=Pickering Signs New Three Year Deal |url=https://www.crewealex.net/news/2020/september/pixie-new-three-year-deal/ |website=Crewe Alexandra F.C. |accessdate=2020-09-04 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117084453/https://www.crewealex.net/news/2020/september/pixie-new-three-year-deal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2020年12月因為[[黃添喜|黃添喜]]離隊而成為球隊隊長<ref name="CAFC-24Dec2020">{{cite news |title=Pixie Honoured To Be Named Captain In Ng Absence |url=https://www.crewealex.net/news/2020/december/pixie-captain/ |access-date=2021-02-12 |work=CreweAlex.net |date=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2022-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220208035630/https://www.crewealex.net/news/2020/december/pixie-captain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年1月，他轉投[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布莱克本流浪者]]並簽約四年半，但首半年以外借方式留在克魯<ref name="BBC-01Feb2021">{{cite news |title=Harry Pickering: Blackburn Rovers sign Crewe Alexandra defender on four-and-a-half year deal |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/55888498 |access-date=2021-02-01 |work=BBC Sport |date=2021-02-01 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506054311/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/55888498 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

